Announcing CppCon 2025 - Join C++ Developers, C++ Programmers and C++ Experts for the C++ Conference September 13–19 2025
---

CppCon 2025 September 13-19: The Premier C++ Conference for the C++ Community!

CppCon is the ultimate gathering for C++ developers, bringing together C++ experts, C++ enthusiasts, and C++ newcomers for a week of learning, networking, and innovation. Held annually in Aurora, Colorado, near Denver, this C++ conference features insightful keynotes by legends like Bjarne Stroustrup and Herb Sutter, as well as talks covering a diverse range of domains—including embedded systems, game development, finance, and more!

What to Expect at CppCon:
-  Keynotes and panels by leading C++ experts
-  Technical presentations on cutting-edge C++ techniques
-  Lightning talks—quick, engaging, and thought-provoking! .
-  Social events and “unconference” sessions for casual discussions and networki
